-- BP says Transocean didn't test blowout shut off
-- 
-- Wed Sep 8, 2010 11:19am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/09/08/us-bp-rig-report-idUSTRE68739Q20100908

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - BP Plc officials said on Wednesday there was "no indication" that Transocean Ltd tested the automatic shut off function on the blowout preventer before it was used on the Deepwater Horizon drilling rig the company leased to BP. 

 (Reporting by  Ayesha Rascoe )